{"title":"长河激荡过轻舟  为建立海南省、海南经济特区而作","authors":["许士杰"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":4,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长河激荡过轻舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为建立海南省、海南经济特区而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许士杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长河激荡过轻舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机遇瞬间难再求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上徘徊未捷足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空观流水去悠悠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缆绳紧系制轻舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每溢豪情视水流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赐得上方刀一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光断索趁风游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越峻峰海拔高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从低起跑倍辛劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讥言赞语微风过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健步毋停意气豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啧啧何求事事周，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披荆斩棘岂停留？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"途长道曲多颠簸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赖有飞轮滚不休！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休夸五岳入胸襟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛却铢锱计较心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里有私多芥蒂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中无己尽知音。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}